You\u2019re ready to enjoy some delicious meals and even save some money while you do it! Wow, you\u2019re awesome!!

Hello, sushi lovers!
At Yamamoto Sushi, we take great pride in preparing the freshest, most delicious sushi for our customers. Today, we\u2019re excited to offer a special 5 pa\u2019 las 12 package, perfect for anyone looking to enjoy high-quality sushi while helping to reduce food waste.
Inside this package, you\u2019ll find a delightful selection of our chef\u2019s favorites, including:
Freshly made nigiri (tuna, salmon, shrimp) with perfectly seasoned rice Assorted maki rolls, combining classic flavors like avocado, cucumber, and crab A few pieces of our signature rolls that vary daily based on availability, always a wonderful surprise! A small side of edamame or seaweed salad for that extra touch of freshness
We guarantee you\u2019ll receive a generous assortment of sushi that\u2019s just as delicious as what we serve in-house. This is our way of giving back to the community while ensuring nothing goes to waste. Enjoy it at a fraction of the price and discover the heart of Yamamoto Sushi with every bite.
Thank you for helping us on our mission to reduce food waste and enjoy amazing sushi at the same time!
